                  <objectDesc>
                     <supportDesc>
                        <support>1 papyrus ; 8.5 x 7 cm.</support>
                        <condition>
                           <ab type="conservation">Light-brown papyrus with a darker patch in the center. This papyrus is regularly cut on all sides. It is completely preserved except for a sma abrasion in the lower left side of the papyrus.</ab>
                        </condition>
                     </supportDesc>
                     <layoutDesc>
                        <layout>
                           <ab type="lines">1-9</ab>
                           <ab type="recto-verso">Source of description: Recto</ab>
                        </layout>
                     </layoutDesc>
                  </objectDesc>
                  <handDesc>
                     <p>Written with a very regular cursive. Of the left and bottom margins somewhat more than 1 cm. remains. The right side of the column, on which were recorded the wages paid to the workers, has been lost. To the left of the last line of writing, at the edge of the papyrus and extending into the margin, are amorphous remnants of a preceding column.</p>
